      <title>消息人士称，瑞银投资银行家陈长浩已离开瑞士银行亚太团队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/ubs-investment-banker-changhao-chen-leaves-swiss-lender-s-apac-team-sources-say</link>
